org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.relation

      • org.apache.ctakes.typesystem.type.relation.Relation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttributeRelation, BinaryTextRelation, CollectionTextRelation, ElementRelation, SemanticRoleRelation

    public class Relation
extends TOP
    A superclass for semantic relationships between Elements. For example, one might consider TemporalRelations or UMLSRelations between a Medication and a Disorder. The "category" feature indicates what kind of relation it is. Updated by JCasGen Wed Sep 30 11:06:15 EDT 2015 XML source: /Users/pei/workspace/apache-ctakes/3.2.2/ctakes-ytex-uima/target/jcasgen/typesystem.xml
